{"tid":773769,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"EasyJet cancel flight 賠償無下文","createTime":"2018-08-09T20:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T04:03:02.000Z","uid":43228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2a6de42e93484ef1286cb9fc8be1c7dabb5f9619","tid":773769,"uid":43228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T20:36:55.000Z","msg":"5月時係easyJet 訂左英國去德國嘅機票 去到機場時顯示Delay 等左4個鐘之後班機仲要cancel左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後佢地啲staff咁叫曬啲人出關 但又無講點解班機cancel左 <br />\n<br />\n出到去佢地個Counter問 啲staff就話最快嘅下一班機要下星期先有位 叫啲客book其他公司再同佢地claim返差額同埋住宿 <br />\n<br />\n搞左好耐 其實都差唔多成夜晚11點幾 之後仲要麻煩個fd係佢果到住多晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我第二日就book左第二間airline， 因為即日訂 搞到要成3000幾蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n因為都仲係學生 所以去到德國之後拿拿臨上easyjet個網填form賠償 過左十幾日後（六月中）收到佢地confirm賠償嘅E-Mail 叫我比Bank acc資料佢地 就會係10日內過返數比我<br />\n<br />\n點解我比左資料佢之後 到而家八月一蚊都未收到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n七月頭見仲未收到錢 所以都email reply返handle 我個case個staff 問下佢process成點， 點知係無人覆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以七月尾再填online份form睇下有無cs可以幫手check <br />\n<br />\n第一次就收到佢地cs電話 話會幫我搵返相關同事搞 叫我等佢地同事覆<br />\n<br />\n點知過左一個星期之後都無收過任何相關同事電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n所以再填form問 點知今次連cs都唔覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n尋日再email問多次 點知都係無人覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為我仲係學生 只不過去歐洲exchange  所以其實三千幾蚊對我黎講都算大數目 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而我今個月就會返香港 所以幾希望可以係返香港前搞掂件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知你地有無人都試過同easyJet claim 錢？ 可唔可以同我講下你地claim錢嘅程序係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f48ee72f2bbc561e54f42038cd2857c8e9777dac","tid":773769,"uid":43228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T04:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}